Profile of Douglas Tough 





 


Douglas Tough

 

Dir., CEO, MD - Ansell Ltd.

 


Douglas Tough Email :
Please login 

 

Company Name : 
Ansell Ltd. 

 

Company Website : 
www.ansell.com 

 

Company Address : 
678 Victoria St., Richmond, ,Australia, 


 


Douglas Tough Profile :
Dir., CEO, MD - Ansell Ltd. 

 


Douglas Tough Biography :


Mr. Tough joined Ansell on 11th May and became Chief Executive Officer, and a Director of Ansell Ltd. on July 1st, 2004. Prior to joining Ansell, Mr. Tough, a dual citizen of Canada and USA, spent 17 years with Cadbury Schweppes plc in a number of international and domestic leadership roles, most recently as President and Chief Executive Officer of its largest division worldwide, DrPepper/Seven Up, North America. Mr. Tough has also had some 12 years experience with Procter & Gamble in various sales and marketing assignments. Mr. Tough holds an MBA from the University of Western Ontario, London, Ontario, Canada, and a BBA - University of Kentucky, Lexington, Kentucky, USA. 

 


