hoose from a huge selection of classic comedies, dramas and westerns featuring the greatest stars in the history of Hollywood. Immerse into a classic war story or lose yourself in a masterful thriller that keeps you on the edge of your seat. Animation: Surprise your little ones with their favorite cartoons on DVD and they're likely to have them on repeat all day long. We have a selection of animation DVDs suitable for all ages and preferences, so you can easily find a favorite one for each of your kids. Romance: Surprising your loved one with a nice dinner and a good romantic comedy or drama is very easy thanks to our huge selection of romance movies on DVD. Pick a classic that you ll both enjoy watching again, or go for a new release to find out the happy ending to yet another love story. Documentaries: From nature and wildlife to performing arts, there s a world of documentaries in our DVD collection to keep you well-informed and entertained at the same time. Comedy: Discover the funniest movies released over the last decades, and enjoy witty writing, memorable puns and enjoyable plots the entire family can take great pleasure in watching. Lovers of stand-up comedy can also find a well-stocked section of DVDs. Horror: Whether Halloween is near or you simply feel like watching something scary, you can find a multitude of horror titles on DVD at Walmart. From timeless stories to new additions, enjoy countless titles featuring monsters, serial killers, vampires or zombies.  Foreign: Discover masterpieces of international cinematography on DVD and make a good impression in a conversation when you mention cult movies that have made history. Our selection of foreign movies includes titles from Europe, Asia and more. Music: If you couldn t make it to your favorite pop or rock star live concert, the DVD release will partially make up for it. Alternatively, enjoy classical music concerts and ballet from around the world. Top movies and TV shows bundles Save money and make sure you don t miss an episode by purchasing your favorite TV show on DVD. Most popular TV shows are available in box sets, so you can easily purchase all the series and even get extra perks such as never-before-seen scenes or making-of featurettes. Blockbuster movie franchises are also available in bundles or box sets so you can enhance your collection with ease. Understanding DVD ratings Not all DVDs are suitable for the entire family, so pay attention to ratings when you purchase a new title. G-rated movies are intended for general audiences, and they don t include any nudity, violence or substance-abuse scenes. PG movies may contain material that isn't suitable for children, whereas a movie with a PG-13 rating isn't suitable for children under 13. Rated R movies contain strong language, violence, or nudity, while movies with an NC-17 rating aren't suitable for those under 18.Show moreElectrode, Comp-147384893, DC-prod-dfw2, ENV-prod-a, PROF-PROD, VER-1.16.0, SHA-a61be39c429b9ad89de35da485c799e426355f1c, CID-


